NAME

DateTime::Locale::ia_001 - Locale data examples for the Interlingua World (ia-001) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Interlingua World locale.

Date Formats

Full 

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = martedi le 5 de februario 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = venerdi le 22 de decembre 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = sabbato le 15 de septembre -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 de februario 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 de decembre 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 de septembre -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 feb 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 dec 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 sep -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05-02-2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22-12-1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15-09--10
